data.description:
Welcome to this beautifully updated family home, boasting five bedrooms and 4 1/2 bathrooms. Situated in highly sought-after Berkshire, this property offers the perfect blend of functionality, comfort, and modern elegance.
The covered front porch will be the perfect place to rock and chat with neighbors. 
Upon entering, you will be greeted by an inviting foyer that leads to the spacious and open concept living areas. The adjacent dining area is perfect for hosting dinner parties or enjoying everyday meals.
The updated kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, & ample storage space. The breakfast nook provides a cozy spot to enjoy morning coffee or casual meals with a view of the screen porch and spacious fenced in flat backyard.
The spacious primary suite is off of the kitchen with a gorgeous ensuite bathroom featuring a soaking tub under the window and a walk-in closet. 
The main level also includes a versatile room that can be used as a home office, study, or playroom, offering flexibility to suit your family's needs. A convenient half bathroom completes the main level.
Ascending to the upper level, you will find the three additional well-appointed bedrooms and two full bathrooms provide plenty of space for a growing family or accommodating guests.
The fully finished walkout basement offers endless possibilities, with a spacious recreational area that can be transformed into a home theater, gym, or additional living space. A full bathroom on this level adds convenience and functionality.
The drive under two car garage is accessed down here. 
The roof is brand new along with the freshly painted exterior, this home is ready for you to move you things right into.
